The '''Eolica Istria Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Istria]], [[Constanţa County]], [[Romania]]. It will consist of two individual wind farms connected together. It will have 37 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.edch.ch/projects/descriptions.shtml Eolica Dobrogea to build wind farm in the Dobrogea region] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210014204/http://edch.ch/projects/descriptions.shtml |date=2009-02-10 }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 MW which will deliver up to 74 MW of power, enough to power over 47,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$75 million.

